Package pt.ua.p2utils Description

This package contains classes that implement several types of the elementary data structures studied in Programming 2.

linked lists, sorted linked lists, stacks, queues, key-value lists implementing dictionaries, hash tables implementing dictionaries, binary search trees implementing dictionaries.

Each is a generic type that accepts a type parameter stating the type of elements it will store.
